+ ./prog -i 1b
myint is 512 1

+ ./prog -i 1k
myint is 1024 1

+ ./prog -i 1g
myint is 1073741824 1

+ ./prog -i 1t
prog: unable to convert '-i 1t': Numerical argument out of domain

+ ./prog -i -1b
